 zapravo,

1309
00:42:24,360 --> 00:42:25,460
 mi doživljamo

1310
00:42:25,460 --> 00:42:26,120
 zatvoreno,

1311
00:42:26,120 --> 00:42:26,480
 odnosno,

1312
00:42:26,480 --> 00:42:27,520
 ništa se neće

1313
00:42:27,520 --> 00:42:28,160
 promijeniti.

1314
00:42:28,580 --> 00:42:29,740
 Ono što je tu sad problem

1315
00:42:29,740 --> 00:42:32,920
 kad mi počinjemo

1316
00:42:32,920 --> 00:42:34,120
 pristajati na očaj,

1317
00:42:34,120 --> 00:42:36,580
 mi automatski

1318
00:42:36,580 --> 00:42:38,740
 u svom životu

1319
00:42:38,740 --> 00:42:40,060
 počinjemo

1320
00:42:40,060 --> 00:42:41,720
 razlučivat

1321
00:42:41,720 --> 00:42:42,960
 laž

1322
00:42:42,960 --> 00:42:44,200
 koju nam džao podmeće

1323
00:42:44,200 --> 00:42:44,960
 kao istinu.

1324
00:42:44,960 --> 00:42:47,060
 Kako se to očito je?

1325
00:42:47,060 --> 00:42:48,360
 Pa na ovaj način.

1326
00:42:48,360 --> 00:42:49,440
 Nikad ništa od mene.

1327
00:42:49,440 --> 00:42:50,840
 Ja sam glup,

1328
00:42:50,840 --> 00:42:52,100
 nikad se neće ženti,

1329
00:42:52,100 --> 00:42:53,240
 nikad se neće udati.

1330
00:42:53,240 --> 00:42:54,700
 Ja sam fullo svoje vrijeme,

1331
00:42:54,700 --> 00:42:55,700
 ja sam promašao

1332
00:42:55,700 --> 00:42:56,960
 svoj svećanički poziv.

1333
00:42:58,580 --> 00:43:01,320
 I to postaje istina.

1334
00:43:01,320 --> 00:43:02,900
 Kako će se nakon toga

1335
00:43:02,900 --> 00:43:03,780
 volja pokrenuti?

1336
00:43:03,780 --> 00:43:11,440
 I to mi ovoj našoj

1337
00:43:11,440 --> 00:43:13,360
 terminologiji poznajemo

1338
00:43:13,360 --> 00:43:14,700
 pod unutarnje zavijete.

1339
00:43:14,700 --> 00:43:17,620
 To su ti teška uvjerenja

1340
00:43:17,620 --> 00:43:19,040
 koje smo mi izrekli

1341
00:43:19,040 --> 00:43:19,640
 nad sobom

1342
00:43:19,640 --> 00:43:21,200
 i koje mi zaista vjerujemo.

1343
00:43:21,200 --> 00:43:22,620
 Možda ne svjesno,

1344
00:43:22,620 --> 00:43:25,220
 kada ne našao

1345
00:43:25,220 --> 00:43:25,760
 kad dođeš,

1346
00:43:25,760 --> 00:43:26,760
 a u srcu vrijede

1347
00:43:26,760 --> 00:43:27,880
 taj vrijednostni sustav.

1348
00:43:28,120 --> 00:43:29,520
 Tako je bilo i kod mene.

1349
00:43:29,520 --> 00:43:33,060
 Dok sam bio mlad

1350
00:43:33,060 --> 00:43:35,320
 i moji se...

1351
00:43:35,320 --> 00:43:39,700
 Dok sam bio mlad

1352
00:43:39,700 --> 00:43:40,780
 i...

1353
00:43:40,780 --> 00:43:44,440
 Moji najbliži prijatelj

1354
00:43:44,440 --> 00:43:45,180
 su se poženili

1355
00:43:45,180 --> 00:43:46,120
 i ja osto sam.

1356
00:43:46,120 --> 00:43:49,180
 I sad ja na faksu

1357
00:43:49,180 --> 00:43:53,680
 ide život nekako,

1358
00:43:53,680 --> 00:43:55,320
 zajednica, služenje, sve.

1359
00:43:55,320 --> 00:43:58,760
 i sve do jednog trenutka

1360
00:43:58,760 --> 00:44:01,320
 vidio sam da nema nikako pomaka

1361
00:44:01,320 --> 00:44:02,620
 na tom ljubavnom području

1362
00:44:02,620 --> 00:44:03,940
 i onda sam došao na klanjanje

1363
00:44:03,940 --> 00:44:06,120
 i počeo sam Bogu to predavat

1364
00:44:06,120 --> 00:44:07,060
 kao što bi svaki put,

1365
00:44:07,060 --> 00:44:07,700
 gospodine, predajem ti,

1366
00:44:07,700 --> 00:44:08,260
 molim te da nađem.

1367
00:44:08,740 --> 00:44:10,700
 i dođe,

1368
00:44:10,700 --> 00:44:12,200
 i dolazi trenutak

1369
00:44:12,200 --> 00:44:14,180
 kad mi gospodin pokazuje istinu

1370
00:44:14,180 --> 00:44:15,180
 da sam se,

1371
00:44:15,180 --> 00:44:17,040
 da sam stvorio

1372
00:44:17,040 --> 00:44:19,640
 lažnu sliku o Bogu,

1373
00:44:19,640 --> 00:44:20,300
 a to je

1374
00:44:20,300 --> 00:44:21,320
 da on ne želi

1375
00:44:21,320 --> 00:44:23,680
 ono što ja želim.

1376
00:44:23,680 --> 00:44:26,040
 Da on ne želi sa mnom,

1377
00:44:26,040 --> 00:44:28,000
 ne želi mi dat

1378
00:44:28,000 --> 00:44:29,860
 ono što,

1379
00:44:29,860 --> 00:44:30,560
 evo,

1380
00:44:30,560 --> 00:44:32,400
 što ga ja kao sin tražim.

1381
00:44:34,140 --> 00:44:37,020
 i baš se sjećam tog trenutka

1382
00:44:37,020 --> 00:44:38,340
 kad je ta laž,

1383
00:44:38,340 --> 00:44:40,660
 nekako vratilo mi se sjećanje,

1384
00:44:40,660 --> 00:44:42,460
 kad je ta laž ušla u moj život

1385
00:44:42,460 --> 00:44:46,260
 i tad je u tom trenutku

1386
00:44:46,260 --> 00:44:48,560
 sam se pokajao što sam povjerao tu laž,

1387
00:44:48,560 --> 00:44:50,000
 odrekao se te laži,

1388
00:44:50,000 --> 00:44:52,900
 slomio nad svojim životom

1389
00:44:52,900 --> 00:44:55,980
 i očajanje koje je vladalo u mom životu

1390
00:44:55,980 --> 00:44:57,780
 na tom ljubavnom području

1391
00:44:57,780 --> 00:44:59,900
 se promijenilo za dva tjedna

1392
00:44:59,900 --> 00:45:01,620
 kad sam upoznao svoj bivšu djevojku

1393
00:45:01,620 --> 00:45:02,480
 a sadašnju ženu.

1394
00:45:02,480 --> 00:45:10,480
 Treća stvar,

1395
00:45:10,480 --> 00:45:12,220
 ću malo požurtiti,

1396
00:45:12,220 --> 00:45:14,240
 treća stvar je

1397
00:45:14,240 --> 00:45:15,620
 nepostojanost,

1398
00:45:15,620 --> 00:45:18,400
 odnosno stalna potreba

1399
00:45:18,400 --> 00:45:19,080
 za promjenu.

1400
00:45:19,080 --> 00:45:22,520
 Dugotrajnost u ovom slučaju

1401
00:45:22,520 --> 00:45:24,520
 postaje ono što je nama nepodnošljivo.

1402
00:45:24,520 --> 00:45:25,860
 Ne možemo mi izdržati

1403
00:45:25,860 --> 00:45:28,860
 tu dugotrajnost neke odluke

1404
00:45:28,860 --> 00:45:29,920
 koje smo donijeli

1405
00:45:29,920 --> 00:45:31,920
 koja treba trajati.

1406
00:45:31,920 --> 00:45:34,660
 Zato tu čovjek pribjegava

1407
00:45:34,660 --> 00:45:36,460
 stalno nekoj novosti života.

1408
00:45:36,460 --> 00:45:38,820
 Ne da je Bože da malo dublje uđem.

1409
00:45:38,820 --> 00:45:42,280
 Uvijek samo da sam u pličaku.

1410
00:45:42,280 --> 00:45:45,880
 Znači, tu se u tom slučaju

1411
00:45:45,880 --> 00:45:47,400
 kod te nestalnosti

1412
00:45:47,400 --> 00:45:49,400
 i potrebe za stalnom promjenom

1413
00:45:49,400 --> 00:45:51,360
 čovjek ne bira svoju promjenu

1414
00:45:51,360 --> 00:45:52,040
 zbog rasta.

1415
00:45:52,040 --> 00:45:54,340
 Nego je bira samo

1416
00:45:54,340 --> 00:45:55,900
 iz razloga da pobjegne.

1417
00:45:55,900 --> 00:45:58,240
 I čovjek

1418
00:45:58,240 --> 00:46:00,420
 nigdje ne ostaje dovoljno dugo

1419
00:46:00,420 --> 00:46:01,600
 da bi sazrio.

1420
00:46:01,600 --> 00:46:07,340
 Di to vidimo

1421
00:46:07,340 --> 00:46:08,520
 u današnjem svijetu?

1422
00:46:08,520 --> 00:46:09,780
 Pa to vidimo upravo

1423
00:46:09,780 --> 00:46:11,780
 u tome kako se mladi,

1424
00:46:11,780 --> 00:46:13,480
 a i sve više stari ljudi

1425
00:46:13,480 --> 00:46:14,760
 odnose prema poslu.

1426
00:46:16,520 --> 00:46:18,320
 Nema, to se radi po mjesec, dva,

1427
00:46:18,320 --> 00:46:20,580
 od tog je dva, tri tjedna bolovanje.

1428
00:46:20,580 --> 00:46:25,260
 Svako malo se stvarno mijenje posle.

1429
00:46:25,260 --> 00:46:26,600
 Ja opet sad na drugom poslu

1430
00:46:26,600 --> 00:46:28,460
 od nekog nisam sreo dva tjedna.

1431
00:46:28,460 --> 00:46:29,560
 Nije uspjelo to,

1432
00:46:29,560 --> 00:46:30,820
 našao sam već nešto drugo.

1433
00:46:30,820 --> 00:46:34,520
 To je stvarno,

1434
00:46:34,520 --> 00:46:37,300
 postoje tu razno razni razlozi

1435
00:46:37,300 --> 00:46:38,080
 zašto je tako

1436
00:46:38,080 --> 00:46:39,480
 i tržište rada je tako.

1437
00:46:40,120 --> 00:46:41,480
 to stvarno sve je istina,

1438
00:46:41,480 --> 00:46:42,240
 ali trebamo pogledati

1439
00:46:42,240 --> 00:46:43,020
 gdje sam ja tu

1440
00:46:43,020 --> 00:46:44,920
 i šta je na moj rast.

1441
00:46:44,920 --> 00:46:51,340
 Mnogi, evo,

1442
00:46:51,340 --> 00:46:53,460
 dođu do pete godine,

1443
00:46:53,460 --> 00:46:54,880
 skoro daju sve ispite,

1444
00:46:54,880 --> 00:46:56,080
 ne završe fakultet.

1445
00:46:56,080 --> 00:46:57,140
 Ne znam se,

1446
00:46:57,140 --> 00:46:58,340
 uopće ne postoje razlog

1447
00:46:58,340 --> 00:47:00,140
 zašto se to ne završi.

1448
00:47:00,140 --> 00:47:01,940
 Onda, isto tako,

1449
00:47:01,940 --> 00:47:05,420
 di to vidimo možda u svom životu.

1450
00:47:05,420 --> 00:47:06,340
 Ako smo mi odluči

1451
00:47:06,340 --> 00:47:08,540
 da ćemo moliti 30 minuta,

1452
00:47:08,540 --> 00:47:10,100
 pa zašto onda moliš 20 minuta?

1453
00:47:10,120 --> 00:47:10,400
 23.

1454
00:47:10,400 --> 00:47:12,460
 Zašto?

1455
00:47:12,460 --> 00:47:14,420
 Ti sada minuta,

1456
00:47:14,420 --> 00:47:16,160
 toliko te unervozi,

1457
00:47:16,160 --> 00:47:17,220
 toliko postaneš,

1458
00:47:17,220 --> 00:47:18,600
 ne znaš gdje si,

1459
00:47:18,600 --> 00:47:19,280
 ne znaš štabi,

1460
00:47:19,280 --> 00:47:21,100
 jednostavno moraš šmugnuti,

1461
00:47:21,100 --> 00:47:22,140
 moraš pobjeći.

1462
00:47:22,140 --> 00:47:24,040
 I to si opravdaš

1463
00:47:24,040 --> 00:47:25,460
 na milion dobrih načina.

1464
00:47:25,460 --> 00:47:27,680
 Kako smo mi dobri opravdavanje u sebi.

1465
00:47:27,680 --> 00:47:33,360
 Zatim imamo dosadu

1466
00:47:33,360 --> 00:47:34,120
 i zasićenost.

1467
00:47:34,120 --> 00:47:37,480
 Dosada nije manjak sadržaja,

1468
00:47:37,480 --> 00:47:38,580
 složili smo se na početku,

1469
00:47:38,580 --> 00:47:39,440
 predajem da im ih ima

1470
00:47:39,440 --> 00:47:41,480
 i previše,

1471
00:47:41,480 --> 00:47:42,660
 nego je dosada u tome

1472
00:47:42,660 --> 00:47:43,880
 što mi ne prihvaćamo

1473
00:47:43,880 --> 00:47:45,240
 njihov smisao.

1474
00:47:45,240 --> 00:47:46,400
 I upravo iz toga

1475
00:47:46,400 --> 00:47:47,580
 su nam potrebni,

1476
00:47:47,580 --> 00:47:49,560
 potrebno da imamo

1477
00:47:49,560 --> 00:47:51,140
 niz, niz kompenzacija

1478
00:47:51,140 --> 00:47:52,360
 kako ćemo mi iskoristiti

1479
00:47:52,360 --> 00:47:53,360
 tu dosadu.

1480
00:47:53,360 --> 00:47:56,780
 kako ćemo je na neki način

1481
00:47:56,780 --> 00:47:58,840
 utažiti i tu dolazimo

1482
00:47:58,840 --> 00:48:00,400
 do jednog problema,

1483
00:48:00,400 --> 00:48:02,380
 jer nam se srce postalo toliko tromo,

1484
00:48:02,380 --> 00:48:04,160
 da mi prema ničemu ne možemo

1485
00:48:04,160 --> 00:48:05,760
 izkazati neko čuđenje

1486
00:48:05,760 --> 00:48:08,920
 prema Bogu posebno

1487
00:48:08,920 --> 00:48:10,380
 i još gore, ne možemo

1488
00:48:10,380 --> 00:48:11,040
 za hvalnost.

1489
00:48:11,040 --> 00:48:11,420
 Zašto?

1490
00:48:11,480 --> 00:48:12,700
 zato što je nama sve poznato.

1491
00:48:12,700 --> 00:48:14,060
 Mi sve znamo

1492
00:48:14,060 --> 00:48:16,520
 i toliko smo jednostavno

1493
00:48:16,520 --> 00:48:20,060
 zasićeni sa svime

1494
00:48:20,060 --> 00:48:21,040
 da je jednostavno ono.

1495
00:48:21,040 --> 00:48:21,940
 E sad,

1496
00:48:21,940 --> 00:48:23,280
 u toj dosadi

1497
00:48:23,280 --> 00:48:25,620
 čovjek će napraviti svašta.

1498
00:48:28,020 --> 00:48:31,140
 i jako često mi dolaze ljudi

1499
00:48:31,140 --> 00:48:32,640
 koji imaju previše

1500
00:48:32,640 --> 00:48:33,860
 i previše vremena

1501
00:48:33,860 --> 00:48:34,760
 baviti se sobom.

1502
00:48:34,760 --> 00:48:36,980
 Evo, baš sam sad došao

1503
00:48:36,980 --> 00:48:37,960
 sa devetog kruga

1504
00:48:37,960 --> 00:48:39,180
 igracijanskih vježbi.

1505
00:48:39,180 --> 00:48:41,200
 To je deveta godina sad,

1506
00:48:41,200 --> 00:48:41,860
 evo,

1507
00:48:41,860 --> 00:48:43,840
 svašta sam novo otkrio

1508
00:48:43,840 --> 00:48:44,280
 o sebi.

1509
00:48:44,280 --> 00:48:46,400
 A kada ga pitaš

1510
00:48:46,400 --> 00:48:47,300
 za realni život,

1511
00:48:47,300 --> 00:48:49,180
 samo okrene temu,

1512
00:48:49,180 --> 00:48:50,320
 jer ne želi o tom govoriti,

1513
00:48:50,320 --> 00:48:51,180
 zašto ćeš ga susret

1514
00:48:51,180 --> 00:48:51,940
 sa istinom o sebi,

1515
00:48:51,940 --> 00:48:52,420
 nego ne,

1516
00:48:52,420 --> 00:48:55,360
 samo neke neko drugi kriv,

1517
00:48:55,360 --> 00:48:55,940
 roditelji,

1518
00:48:55,940 --> 00:48:56,640
 ne, ne, ne znam

1519
00:48:56,640 --> 00:48:57,440
 ko je njega uništio

1520
00:48:57,440 --> 00:48:58,280
 za život

1521
00:48:58,280 --> 00:48:59,320
 i ne može

1522
00:48:59,320 --> 00:49:00,840
 preuzeti odgovornost

1523
00:49:00,840 --> 00:49:02,260
 da se suoči

1524
00:49:02,260 --> 00:49:03,180
 sa svijetom vani.

1525
00:49:03,180 --> 00:49:04,880
 Neko samo kopa

1526
00:49:04,880 --> 00:49:05,660
 po svojim ranama.

1527
00:49:05,660 --> 00:49:08,180
 I takvim ljudima

1528
00:49:08,180 --> 00:49:08,980
 često kažem

1529
00:49:08,980 --> 00:49:10,720
 aj malo

1530
00:49:10,720 --> 00:49:11,720
 aj ti razmisliti

1531
00:49:11,720 --> 00:49:13,800
 jel ti u svom životu

1532
00:49:13,800 --> 00:49:14,720
 razmatraš

1533
00:49:14,720 --> 00:49:16,000
 svoje rane

1534
00:49:16,000 --> 00:49:17,180
 ili kristove rane?

1535
00:49:17,180 --> 00:49:19,340
 Koji će tebe rane spati?

1536
00:49:19,340 --> 00:49:20,420
 Tvoje rane ili kristove?

1537
00:49:20,420 --> 00:49:26,860
 Ono

1538
00:49:26,860 --> 00:49:28,600
 što

1539
00:49:28,600 --> 00:49:32,060
 nam tu može doći kao rješenje

1540
00:49:32,060 --> 00:49:34,460
 je upravo dokolica.

1541
00:49:34,460 --> 00:49:36,020
 Kaže knjiga Svjerohova

1542
00:49:36,020 --> 00:49:38,900
 u dokolice je mudro zakonoznanca

1543
00:49:38,900 --> 00:49:39,760
 i kod poslova

1544
00:49:39,760 --> 00:49:41,900
 slobodan

1545
00:49:41,900 --> 00:49:42,760
 postaje mudar.

1546
00:49:42,760 --> 00:49:44,980
 Nama treba

1547
00:49:44,980 --> 00:49:45,920
 jedan vid

1548
00:49:45,920 --> 00:49:47,260
 dokolice

1549
00:49:47,260 --> 00:49:48,660
 u pozitivnom smislu

1550
00:49:48,660 --> 00:49:49,500
 riječ dosada

1551
00:49:49,500 --> 00:49:51,440
 da nam bude dosadno.

1552
00:49:52,520 --> 00:49:52,920
 zašto?

1553
00:49:52,920 --> 00:49:54,840
 Zato što tek u toj dokolici

1554
00:49:54,840 --> 00:49:56,040
 čovjek može

1555
00:49:56,040 --> 00:49:57,720
 se pozabaviti

1556
00:49:57,720 --> 00:49:58,060
 svojim

1557
00:49:58,060 --> 00:49:59,740
 egzistencijalnim pitanjima.

1558
00:50:00,540 --> 00:50:01,140
 tko sam ja?

1559
00:50:01,980 --> 00:50:03,060
 zašto sam ja ovdje?

1560
00:50:05,520 --> 00:50:06,700
 gdje ja idem?

1561
00:50:07,260 --> 00:50:08,500
 kog ja volim?

1562
00:50:08,500 --> 00:50:10,320
 Što ja želim u životu?

1563
00:50:10,320 --> 00:50:11,800
 Ko voli mene?

1564
00:50:12,620 --> 00:50:13,620
 To su pitanja

1565
00:50:13,620 --> 00:50:14,980
 koje mogu doći

1566
00:50:14,980 --> 00:50:16,580
 kad otkrijemo

1567
00:50:16,580 --> 00:50:17,740
 taj svijet dokolice.

1568
00:50:17,740 --> 00:50:19,940
 Kad nismo

1569
00:50:19,940 --> 00:50:21,060
